My take
Airbnb needs to keep working on this. It needs to introduce the changes, measure the results and take any complaints of racial discrimination incredibly seriously. Eliminating racial bias out of a platform that relies on its users to make decisions on who they will host will never be easy â€“ racial bias is incredibly prevalent in our society. However, if Airbnb finds that these measures arenâ€™t working, they need to go further.
